    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. The primary experimental dataset (dataVintage 2025-02-17) predates the model revision of 2025-03-10 by approximately three weeks; the team determined that the revision — updating the turbulence-to-viscous stress partitioning coefficient by 4% — was not material to the hemolysis index comparison and that re-execution of the full validation campaign was not warranted. This determination was made by engineering judgment without formal sensitivity analysis linking the revised coefficient to the validation QoI. Overall credibility sufficient for Class II CPB submission at Medium assurance level.",
